Package: restoptr
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to the 'Restopt' ecological restoration planning software
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dimitri Justeau-Allaire, Jeffrey Hanson, Ghislain Vieilledent, Nicolas Rinck, Philippe Vismara, Xavier Lorca, Philippe Birnbaum
Maintainer: Dimitri Justeau-Allaire <dimitri.justeau@gmail.com>
Description:  Interface to the `restopt` ecological restoration planning software,
  which is specifically designed to identify connected, accessible, and compact 
  areas for ecological restoration, with an emphasis on reducing habitat 
  fragmentation and increasing habitat connectivity.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: rJava,
Imports: raster, rgdal, checkmate, utils
URL: https://github.com/dimitri-justeau/restoptr
BugReports: https://github.com/dimitri-justeau/restoptr/issues
